sequenceDiagram
    participant Redis
    participant Worker
    participant PG as PostgreSQL
    participant API
    actor Manager
    actor Staff

    Note over Redis,Staff: SLA Timer Fires (30min elapsed)

    Redis->>Worker: Delayed job fires
    Worker->>PG: SELECT workflow (check status)

    alt Still unresolved
        Worker->>PG: UPDATE workflow (escalated)
        Worker->>PG: INSERT events (sla_breach + escalated)
        Worker->>Redis: Publish escalation alert
        API-->>Manager: Red banner + sound
        API-->>Staff: Card turns red
    else Already resolved
        Worker->>Worker: No-op, discard
    end
